{"tid":1467811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"超突發！！入嚟！！侵話老解已出","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:39.000Z","uid":38293,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5934b30a7f4ba10fb60c8a8a13480d5e5a366408","tid":1467811,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1161325870516264961?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1161325870516264961%3Fs%3D19&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=5b3ea3ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1161325870516264961%3Fs%3D19&h=a282ff8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1161325870516264961?s=19</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aitZAGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaitZAGF.jpg&h=542efc20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b76413efd9e63fad7abd4ede2282148d2e6d70a4","tid":1467811,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3681690ff5ea8ef09cc3e0e0d28cc4926a355c03","tid":1467811,"uid":38293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"天滅中共"},{"pid":"0d78b1a75c451efde02f88ae04840c2dbb49f483","tid":1467811,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cc82999fce3fa665abab275fee752ea4dbcb1b","tid":1467811,"uid":95160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:31.000Z","msg":"文長幫推<br />\n<br />\n機場圍人要屌 但唔該唔好灰唔好割<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466484\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466484</a>"},{"pid":"8980c1081d9024fb08c9a3a5a1aa1f8d1a9d96a7","tid":1467811,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69b18cd0c2445f5cf0b29855b9eb63ae8fd89b5e","tid":1467811,"uid":267942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:35.000Z","msg":"遇鬼時<br />\n<br />\n1）先捉，<br />\n<br />\n2）圍大圈，分隔 同比多d 記者同人映隻鬼，<br />\n<br />\n個個企到密，根本映唔到。<br />\n<br />\n如鬼或自己人有受傷，都要拍片搵在場醫護幫忙<br />\n<br />\n自己傷固之然要醫護， 亦要係記者前問鬼有冇受傷或身體不適，搵在場醫護幫忙做初步檢查，盡番人道立場同道德高地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3）搵記者影記錄，重點指出隻鬼做左乜野犯罪行為如打人，煽動，藏有危險品之類，所以採訪101拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n有物證就映埋物證。同令佢身分曝光，唔好祈望隻鬼會自爆，如果你諗住全世界鏡頭前嚴刑迫供，咁根本係另類送人頭，更何況打死隻鬼，相信佢都唔會講。<br />\n<br />\n闡明你嘅行為係合法性同正當性，同有需要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4）同時搵議員，叫議員處理/議員報警處理。<br />\n相信10多其9都上白車，popo都放人。<br />\n<br />\n重點係，你留住隻鬼冇乜用，只會令現場仲難控制仲亂，好似今日咁，好易比其他鬼去分化，阻醫護阻記者，<br />\n<br />\n如只做1-4，我知大家可能會好嬲，想發洩，但係隻鬼重點係要佢曝光比世界，囉資料，囉更多頻譜，依個先更有利。<br />\n<br />\n你唔好忘記一舉一動既然係鏡頭前，就要有鏡頭禮儀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒有最好的方法，要有改善的辦法"},{"pid":"3792514017c752ea0dfbc35d14062436be9eada8","tid":1467811,"uid":13349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:44.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">「我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。」</code></pre>"},{"pid":"6403d18adb2454c0b5f04085f52a81c0773a6958","tid":1467811,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMYe82i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMYe82i.png&h=751aab96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94ba21a8f08ca79792d5ad06daaf7d98fbc2be2b","tid":1467811,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc533eef542127a79cb2ba82f363050707e5b05","tid":1467811,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6403d18adb2454c0b5f04085f52a81c0773a6958","tid":1467811,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:00.00